race.description: Williams Crane Hire Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: BOMB ROCKY (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Weblec Snip (23.61) in a TG1-4W. Placed at her previous run. Hard to knock her form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Rates on top in this line up. MCIVOR OLLY (7) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Finished in the minors last time when third (28.71) at Bendigo making it back to back placings. Has a good record at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings five times from 10 attempts. Expected to feature again. ADHANA MARTINA (2) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten a nose (31.19) behind Toora Terry at Angle Park. Expected to be in this for a long way. MARLI MOO (4) returns here as an each-way chance.
